	  * Modified TARGET_OS definition for SuSE targets.
	  * Added checking for environment variable PERMISSIVE: If set
	    to yes, then enable -fpermissive gcc/g++ flag 
	    (SASCFLAGS and SASCXXFLAGS).

Version 1.494 - 2009-03-26 (EO)
