Version 1.455 - 2006-06-15 (EO)
-------------
	+ Version for the release track
	  SHAREDVERSION=yes (configure.in)
	  AKA := 7.0.0-Alpha (Make.include.in)
	+ Modified definition of \url command in doc/lib/sasglobal.tex
	  to avoid problems when no prior definition is done, by using
	  \providecommand instead of \renewcommand.

